social_posts.post_text: 🤍 this one is for you guys, and the beautiful memories we created this year. Thank you, from the bottom of my heart, I love you. #2022

🌺 Mahalo Hawaii 🌺

.
.
.
.
.

Such a special trip, to fulfill a long awaited family vacay to the islands to celebrate the wedding of my big brother & his wife 🤍 #lingosatlast
.
.
Although this trip had its difficulties with high emotions from really missing my stepdad, as it was a shared dream before he passed, to teaching the family the intricacies of travel, assuming the role of coordinator & chauffeur among other things. It was perfect and beautiful and the island spoiled us with sun and warmth and ease. 🏝️
.
.
I feel nothing but gratitude returning to the mountains once again. “Ohana means family, 
& family means nobody is left behind or forgotten” ✨

Thank you, ily.

🛩️ Vegas last weekend.. 
.
.
.
.
My first time on a pj, and my first live fight.. 
I love this life 😽

🌵Oops, I forgot to post from Cabo.. 
.
.
.
.
#Mexico #BoatDay #🌞

🤍 To surrender to love 
& all its yearnings, 
is to open to God. 
.
.
& to find clarity,
Comfort and trust
To always continue,
Or begin again.. 
.
.
#DearLover 
#♾️

LA you’re always so good to me 🤍
Big thank you to my angels that show me the best time, every time ✨
